# Env (see `.env.example`)

- `GHL_INBOUND_WEBHOOK_URL` — Lead Connector inbound webhook URL; receives `buildGhlPayload()` JSON from `POST /api/submit-lead`.
- `GHL_PIPELINE_ID` — `pit-…` → payload key `ghlPipelineId`.
- `GHL_LOCATION_ID` → payload key `ghlLocationId`.
- `GHL_PRIVATE_INTEGRATION_TOKEN` — optional REST API only; never client-side.

Align `api/submit-lead.ts` with `lib/leadApi.ts` when changing payload fields.

# Deploy

Vercel: set env vars on the project; build `pnpm run build` from this directory.
